{"tid":1525991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（暗黑兵法）主動反過來投訴某些人校園欺凌！","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:13:48.000Z","uid":300447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9cee15fc7964845d6fc1bb1c99b2846ab2b70a9e","tid":1525991,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:19.000Z","msg":"現在政府吹到咁大，說什麼零容忍，不如開學後先發制人，一般同學主動投訴被某職業子女欺凌！<br />\n<br />\n警察又向子女派發防狼器，就是說所有學生都可以用防狼器。Why not 一般學生每人一個防狼器作警報，警示其他學生不要走近?"},{"pid":"ce514e42855c3b7881bd0b982a61402ebb3013a3","tid":1525991,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=711cfa03\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"943